UNOFFICIAL COPY 26 RS BR 2606
1 A CONCURRENT RESOLUTION adjourning the 2026 Regular Session of the
2 General Assembly sine die.
3 Be it resolved by the Senate of the General Assembly of the Commonwealth of
4 Kentucky, the House of Representatives concurring therein:
5 Section 1. When the Senate and the House of Representatives adjourn on
6 Wednesday, April 15, 2026, they do adjourn sine die, and they shall not convene again
7 until the first occurring of the 2027 Regular Session on Tuesday, January 5, 2027, or an
8 extraordinary session upon call by the Governor.
